title: The North Face Men's Venture Jacket
description: The North Face Men's Venture Jacket. Ready for backcountry storms or everday excursions, this waterproof, breathable hooded jacket is designed to protect you from rain, year round. The HyVent™ 2.5L soft-shell exterior is finished with a dry-touch coating that eliminates the need for a mesh lining.
